{"word":"Mark","slug":"mark","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mark</b> A nephew of Barnabas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=10'>Col 4:10</a><br/> A disciple of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=12'>Act 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=25'>Act 12:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=5'>Act 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=13'>Act 13:13</a><br/> Paul and Barnabas contend concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=39'>Act 15:39</a><br/> A convert of Peter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=13'>1Pe 5:13</a><br/> Fellow-worker with Paul at Rome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=11'>Col 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=11'>2Ti 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=57&chapter=1&verse=24'>Phm 1:24</a>"}]}